query: select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.LastName not like '%[a-zA-Z0-9.- ,:;?!_+=*\/|%()}{<>`~@#$^&№«»]%' and PerC.FirstName not like '%[a-zA-Z0-9.- ,:;?!_+=*\/|%()}{<>`~@#$^&№«»]%' and PerC.MiddleName not like '%[a-zA-Z0-9.- ,:;?!_+=*\/|%()}{<>`~@#$^&№«»]%' and len(PerC.LastName) > 0 and len(PerC.FirstName) > 0 and len(PerC.MiddleName) > 0 and PerC.DeathDate is null
